{"tid":1862945,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"輕鐵天瑞站疑分別發生自燃現象","createTime":"2020-02-05T01:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T05:42:34.000Z","uid":184679,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7030331a075af43c862bc6f1060bb0a5b1317bd2","tid":1862945,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200205/s00001/bcfaa2e5fc49a30569271f02a9af8876.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200205%2Fs00001%2Fbcfaa2e5fc49a30569271f02a9af8876.jpg&h=c42d0c9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方昨晚11時許離開後，再有示威者在天瑞路以輕鐵路軌上的碎石、單車及垃圾桶等雜物堵路，有巴士駛至發現無法通行，乘客需要自行落車徒步離去。<br />\n<br />\n至今日凌晨零時許，多名示威者手持硬物包括士巴拿等工具破壞輕鐵天瑞站設施，又有人將衛生巾貼在入閘機上，噴上懷疑紅色噴漆及以紅筆寫上「全面封關」。約1時，有人向售票機縱火，冒出黑煙，消防到場將火救熄。未幾，有人發現有警車在附近駛過，擔心警方即將包抄，眾人四散。至近2時，未見有防暴警到場。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，輕鐵今早如常服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200205/s00001/1580863956411/%E8%BC%95%E9%90%B5%E5%A4%A9%E7%91%9E%E7%AB%99%E9%81%AD%E7%B8%B1%E7%81%AB%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200205%2Fs00001%2F1580863956411%2F%25E8%25BC%2595%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2591%259E%25E7%25AB%2599%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%25B8%25B1%25E7%2581%25AB%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A3%259E&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3dXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=5abe2ca3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200205%2Fs00001%2F1580863956411%2F%25E8%25BC%2595%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2591%259E%25E7%25AB%2599%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%25B8%25B1%25E7%2581%25AB%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A3%259E&h=28ea5b40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200205/s00001/1580863956411/%E8%BC%95%E9%90%B5%E5%A4%A9%E7%91%9E%E7%AB%99%E9%81%AD%E7%B8%B1%E7%81%AB%E7%